&lt;h2 id="the-empty-mall-effect">The Empty Mall Effect&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Open your favorite job board. Notice the silence? It feels like wandering an abandoned mall: the food court is still lit, a couple of anchor stores survive, but the ground floor, the kiosks, the first rung, is empty. Not because tech collapsed. Because the roles that used to teach beginners were the easiest to automate.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>